extends layout

block content
  .row.text-white
    .col-sm-auto.border.border-secondary.rounded.p-3.bg-dark
      h1.display-1 Should You <b>Ride</b>? 
        script.
          function getWeather() {
            navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition((success, error) => {
              console.log('tried to get location');
              if (error) console.log(error);
              if (success) {
                window.location.href = "/" + success.coords.latitude + "/" + success.coords.longitude;
              }
            });
          }
        a.btn.btn-success(role="button" onclick="getWeather()" style="font-size: 2rem !important; padding: .5rem 2rem") Get Weather
      hr
      h1.display-6.text-info#about Stupid question, YES!
      p.lead.
        Seriously though, before you ride you should consider not only the risks, 
        but also the remarks to being a safe and confident rider while being on the public road. 
        Well this website provides a solution to riders that want to know if they should ride today 
        (based on weather & traffic statistics for your location).
      hr
      h2 For questions, concerns, or suggestions 
        a.btn.btn-outline-warning(href="https://should-you-ride.herokuapp.com/contactus" role="button") Click Here
    include windChillChart.pug


